descriptionHtml:
Hello,
this is the preset of one of the characters i created.
She is called Adriana, sure you can rename her to whatever you want.
There are two variants available, choose the one you like the best, or take both.

"Installation":
Download and extract the file.
Put it in skyrim/Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen/Presets.
Start the game.
To find the preset open the console and type "showracemenu" without the quotes,
then get to the tab "presets", press F9 and if you placed it right it should be in the list.

Required mods:
SKSE
Racemenu
KSHairdos
Eyes of Beauty
Brows/SG Eyebrows (look in the pictures)

Just treat her well :)
I wanted to publish her, because I'll maybe quit skyrim, so everyone can use these presets if he likes too and I can also get it back if i want to continue playing skyrim sometime again.

The credits go to all the authors of the mods used on her and also a big thanks to the author of Racemenu, without this it woudn't have been possible.
